phrases.phrase: 제가 당신이라면 그렇게 안 할 겁니다.
meanings: 의견 말하기 If I were you, I wouldn't do that.
의견 말하기 That's not how I would go about it.
여가활동 What do you do when you're not working at the office?
실용회화-반대 I won't do that if I were you.

vlive.english: I am not going to talk informally!

vlive.korean: 알았어, 안 할 거야, 안 할 거야 - 진짜 하지 마, 진짜...
안 할 거야? - 너는 했잖아 너 초심을 잃은 거야 지금?
vlive.english: You won't? - You did it? You lost your initial resolution?
I'm not going to act cute!

examples.korean: 난 다른 사람들을 돕는 일에 질린 상태였다. 이제부턴 더 이상 아주 좋은 남자는 안 할 작정이었다.
examples.english: I was tired of helping other people. From now on it was no more Mr Nice Guy

examples.korean: 많은 사람들이 결혼을 안 할 결심을 한다.
examples.english: Many people choose not to marry.

examples.korean: 내가 아무한테도 말 안 할 거라는 건 믿어도 돼.
examples.english: You can trust me not to tell anyone.

examples.korean: 안심해도 돼. 아무에게도 말 안 할 테니까.
examples.english: You can rest easy—I’m not going to tell anyone.
